{"tid":623713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地司機扮富商誘港女保險經紀上床換保單 再以性交片勒索今判囚","createTime":"2018-04-10T08:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T18:24:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":315,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"f814c073fb3188d57d521a6a199ee252c45bf876","tid":623713,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"被告張文濤(27歲)今在區院承認兩項勒索罪。法官稱本案罪行差劣，被告令事主擔心，但因事主迅速報警而威脅時間不長，被告亦無向他人發佈片段，故判被告入獄16個月。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，被告在去年 9月8日傍晚在深圳一間酒店與事主見面，洽談一小時後被告聲稱同意投資其中兩個計劃，然後要求與事主性交。事主答應卻不知被告在房內角落擺放了一部手機，拍攝二人做愛過程。完事後事主返港並多次催促被告簽文件及交保費，但未獲回應。<br />\n<br />\n至同月9日下午2時半，被告透過微信向事主發送四段性交片，要求對方付兩萬人民幣以刪除片段，否則他會在網上發佈片段以損壞其聲譽。事主大驚答應，翌日被告約她到沙田大會堂見面，事主隨後報警，最終被告赴約時遭埋伏的警員拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180410/58055917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58055917&d=5v%2FDwfTm9hZZ%2BvngnM%2Ffv54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bb276266\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58055917&h=5935ef6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180410/58055917</a><br />\n<br />\n死蠢，大陸交收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0628c0c45b40310223a8b8aad636feaf1d80ff14","tid":623713,"uid":2054,"like":80,"dislike":3,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"片/老母"},{"pid":"382a8f4f241f2d8c113d05dd3429433304d4a24c","tid":623713,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":47,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/164039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F164039_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e940174e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acb2bd2438540889c6